{
  "stem": "16503.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 309.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She took her clean handkerchief.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She spit on my arm, and she wrapped my arm and was very, very angry at the teacher.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I was terribly embarrassed because I was different than the other kids.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That is one.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not really.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was just this-- what would one call it?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Protect-- being protected.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Today maybe they would call it overprotected.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I have the feeling that in those days, the overprotection, which I-- which I had was so nice that it sustained me all through my life.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That when you then find yourself in the world alone, and alone you are, you kind of cling to the memories of, of the protective times.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was lucky.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I was a very ardent lover of Prague, and it is a beautiful city, you know, structurally and historically and everything.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And everybody who goes there says what a beautiful, beautiful city, and it is.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's got-- it's got the castle and the river running through and of course that National Theatre.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Even in those days, we were taken to it and saw operas and plays.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, we were very culturally brought up, though I was a tomboy and I would try to do other things.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But culturally, we were in a theater in a-- in a-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I don't even remember.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, we went to concerts.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And though I, I went and remember it very well, I don't think at that age-- I must have been very young.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We are now speaking from zero to nine, hey?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "After that, it all, all finished.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I do remember seeing the, the which is by Smetana and the Moldau concert by whoever it is by-- Dvorak is it?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I think so.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
